Riley is a career girl. She will do whatever it takes to get where she wants to be. Working hard for a successful businessman, she has never been offered a raise. She knows her boss is a bit of a pervert and when she plucks up the courage to ask for more money, she is not surprised when it gets sexual - but she didn't expect just how intense this experience was going to get
